==Trivia==
[[File:Postbag from the Hedge - King Black Dragon stamp.png|thumb|King Black Dragon as he appears on the [[Postbag from the Hedge]] stamp.]]
*King Black Dragon appears on one of the seven [[Postbag from the Hedge]] stamps.
*Engaging in combat with the King Black Dragon while not having any form of [[dragonfire]] protection gives unique messages in the player's chatbox when they are harmed by the various types of dragonfire:
**'''Freezing''': {{mes|You're chilled to the bone by the dragon's icy breath!}}
**'''Poison''': {{mes|You're badly scalded by the dragon's toxic breath!}}
**'''Shocking''': {{mes|You're zapped by the dragon's shocking breath!}}
**'''Burning''': {{mes|You're horribly burnt by the dragon's fiery breath!}}
*The King Black Dragon can talk, as seen in [[A Tail of Two Cats]]. During the first part of the final cutscene, when he is visited by [[Bob the cat]], they have a conversation before being interrupted by [[R4ng3rno0b889]].
*The King Black Dragon had a festive override wearing a [[santa hat]], [[purple partyhat]], and [[green partyhat]] during the [[2017 Christmas event/Gallery|2017]], [[2018 Christmas event/Gallery|2018]], [[2019 Christmas event/Gallery|2019]], [[2020 Christmas event/Gallery|2020]], [[2021 Christmas event/Gallery|2021]], [[2022 Christmas event/Gallery|2022]], [[2023 Christmas event/Gallery|2023]], [[2024 Christmas event/Gallery|2024]], and [[2025 Christmas event/Gallery|2025]] Christmas events.
*The King Black Dragon was the strongest monster in ''[[RuneScape Classic]]'' and retained the title until the introduction of ''[[RuneScape 2]]''{{'}}s first new boss, the [[Kalphite Queen]].

